org.littleshoot.proxy

Class BaseChainedProxyTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.littleshoot.proxy.BaseProxyTest
      • org.littleshoot.proxy.BaseChainedProxyTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EncryptedTCPChainedProxyTest, EncryptedUDTChainedProxyTest, UnencryptedTCPChainedProxyTest, UnencryptedUDTChainedProxyTest

    public abstract class BaseChainedProxyTest
extends BaseProxyTest
    Base class for tests that test a proxy chained to a downstream proxy. In addition to the usual assertions, this also asserts that every request sent by the upstream proxy was received by the downstream proxy.
